resources.string: Ivumela lolu hlelo lokusebenza ukuba lufunde izinamathiseli zakho zeMeyili ye-Google.
Ivumela lolu hlelo lokusebenza ukuba luguqule Imeyili yakho ye-Google, kuhlanganise ukuthumela kanye nokususa imeyili.
Vumela loluhlelo lokusebenza lithumele imlayezo ye-Meyli ye-Google ngaphandle kokuvula uhlelo lokusebenza lwe-Meyli ye-Google.
Ukusebenzisa i-Google Mail, udinga i-akhawunti ye-Google.
"Imeyli ye-Googlel yakhelwe ngomqondo wokuba i-imeyli ibe eyokuzibonela ngenhliziyo, elula, futhi ewusizo. Futhi mhlawumbe ejabulisayo."
I-akhawunti %s akuyona i-akhawunti elungile Ye-imeyli ye-Google
